    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Just as Athena Pierce feared, Nobunaga has allied himself with the nefarious Black Wings... "
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "What could he be scheming that he would require their power? Perhaps his forces are weaker than I thought."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The Oda clan was never one to rely on diluting their own power with underhanded deals. It seems unlike him."
      },
      "3": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "And using dark magic to cause chaos in Maple World... where is the rigid, structured warlord I have battled in the past?"
      },
      "4": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "All this thinking is making me hungry. I'd best return to Momijigaoka... maybe that nice fellow Kenshin will have me over for dinner."
      },
